      <div xml:id="timf-acci">
        <head xml:id="timf-acci-Hd1e117">Accidia</head>
        <div xml:id="timf-acci-Dd1e120">
          <head xml:id="timf-acci-Hd1e122">a (1)</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-acci-d1e125">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-acci-Qd1e129">Torpor et ignauia dicunt: si lectioni continuato studio semper insistis, oculorum
        caliginem incurris; si indesinenter lacrimas fundis, ipsos eciam oculos amittis; si
        procellatis uigiliis psalmorum censum persoluis, insaniam capitis acquiris; si cotidiano
        labore te conficis, ad opus spirituale quando consurgis?</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-acci-Qd1e129" xml:id="timf-acci-Rd1e135">Augustinus in libro de conflictu uiciorum et uirtutum.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-acci-Dd1e140">
          <head xml:id="timf-acci-Hd1e142">a (2)</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-acci-d1e145">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-acci-Qd1e149">Accidia est de uirtutum laudabili exercicio utriusque hominis languida
        deiectio.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-acci-Qd1e149" xml:id="timf-acci-Rd1e155">Gregorius in omelia.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-acci-Dd1e160">
          <head xml:id="timf-acci-Hd1e162">b</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-acci-d1e165">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-acci-Qd1e169">Accidia est animi quidam langor cum legere non libet, orare non delectat,
        meditaciones sollicite non sentiuntur.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-acci-Qd1e169" xml:id="timf-acci-Rd1e175">Bernardus in epistolis.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-acci-Dd1e180">
          <head xml:id="timf-acci-Hd1e182">c</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-acci-d1e185">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-acci-Qd1e189">Cum te accidia uel tedio affici sentis, noli propterea diffidere atque desistere a
        studio spirituali, sed iuuantis require manum trahi post te eum obsecrans.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-acci-Qd1e189" xml:id="timf-acci-Rd1e195">Bernardus ibidem (in epistolis).</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-acci-Dd1e201">
          <head xml:id="timf-acci-Hd1e203">d</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-acci-d1e206">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-acci-Qd1e210">Accidia est quidam animi torpor quo quis negligit aliqua bona inchoare aut fastidit
        perficere.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-acci-Qd1e210" xml:id="timf-acci-Rd1e216">Bernardus in sermone.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-acci-Dd1e221">
          <head xml:id="timf-acci-Hd1e223">e</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-acci-d1e226">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-acci-Qd1e230">O homo impudens et imprudens! Milia milium ministrant ei et decies centena
        assistunt ei et tu sedere presumis?</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-acci-Qd1e230" xml:id="timf-acci-Rd1e236">Bernardus ibidem (in sermone).</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-acci-Dd1e241">
          <head xml:id="timf-acci-Hd1e243">f</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-acci-d1e246">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-acci-Qd1e250">Vult et non uult piger; recte pigri uocabulo denotatur qui uult regnare cum Deo, et
        non laborare pro Deo. Delectant premia cum pollicentur; deterrent certamina cum
        iubentur.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-acci-Qd1e250" xml:id="timf-acci-Rd1e256">Beda super Prouerbia libro II.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-acci-Dd1e261">
          <head xml:id="timf-acci-Hd1e263">g</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-acci-d1e266">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-acci-Qd1e270">Non dormientibus prouenit regnum celorum, nec ocio et desidia torpentibus beatitudo
        eternitatis repromittitur.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-acci-Qd1e270" xml:id="timf-acci-Rd1e276">Leo papa in sermone de apparicione.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-acci-Dd1e281">
          <head xml:id="timf-acci-Hd1e283">h</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-acci-d1e286">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-acci-Qd1e290">Accidia circa horam sextam maxime monachum inquietat ut quedam febris ingruens
        tempore prestituto ardentissimos estus accessionum suarum solitis ac statutis horis
        anime inferens egrotanti.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-acci-Qd1e290" xml:id="timf-acci-Rd1e296">Iohannes Cassianus libro X. de institutis monachorum.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-acci-Dd1e301">
          <head xml:id="timf-acci-Hd1e303">i</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-acci-d1e306">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-acci-Qd1e310">Experimento probatum est accidie impugnacionem non declinando fugiendam sed
        resistendo superandam.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-acci-Qd1e310" xml:id="timf-acci-Rd1e316">Idem in eodem libro (Iohannes Cassianus libro X. de institutis monachorum).</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-acci-Dd1e322">
          <head xml:id="timf-acci-Hd1e324">k</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-acci-d1e327">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-acci-Qd1e331">Accidia est solitariis magis experta et in heremo commorantibus infestior hostis ac
        frequens.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-acci-Qd1e331" xml:id="timf-acci-Rd1e337">Idem in eodem libro (Iohannes Cassianus libro X. de institutis monachorum).</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-acci-Dd1e342">
          <head xml:id="timf-acci-Hd1e344">m</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-acci-d1e347">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-acci-Qd1e351">Pigricia est animi inhercia uel fatigacio qua quis bonum inchoatum consummare
        fastidit.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-acci-Qd1e351" xml:id="timf-acci-Rd1e357">Tullius de Tusculanis questionibus.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-acci-Dd1e362">
          <head xml:id="timf-acci-Hd1e364">n</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-acci-d1e367">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-acci-Qd1e371">Luxurioso frugalitas pena est; pigro supplicii loco labor est; desidioso studere
        torqueri est.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-acci-Qd1e371" xml:id="timf-acci-Rd1e377">Seneca epistola LXXII.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-acci-Dd1e382">
          <head xml:id="timf-acci-Hd1e384">o</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-acci-d1e387">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-acci-Qd1e391">Non putant desidiosi posse fieri quicquam quod facere non possunt; ex infirmitate
        sua de uirtute ferunt sentenciam. Nam hec ad que imbecilli sumus dura atque intolleranda
        credimus, tormenta reputantes, uino carere aut prima luce excitari. Non ista difficilia
        sunt sed nos fluidi et enerues sumus.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-acci-Qd1e391" xml:id="timf-acci-Rd1e397">Seneca LXXII. epistola.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-acci-Dd1e402">
          <head xml:id="timf-acci-Hd1e404">p</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-acci-d1e407">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-acci-Qd1e411">Male michi esse malo quam molliter. Si mollis es, paulatim effeminatur animus atque
        in similitudinem ocii sui et pigricie in quam iacet soluitur. Dormio minimum et
        breuissimo sompno utor; satis est michi uigilare desiisse. Aliquando me dormisse scio,
        aliquando suspicor.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-acci-Qd1e411" xml:id="timf-acci-Rd1e417">Seneca XXXIII. epistola.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-acci-Dd1e422">
          <head xml:id="timf-acci-Hd1e424">q</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-acci-d1e427">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-acci-Qd1e431">Nichil agere semper infelicis est optimum.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-acci-Qd1e431" xml:id="timf-acci-Rd1e437">Seneca in prouerbiis.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
